 genuinely well-made, and feels handcrafted. You’re experiencing something someone has made, not something a company has reskinned. I’ve never written a review before, but this game deserves one. Absolutely recommend” - Dgrub</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"No I don't think I'll ever play your game, and more importantly, let's return to talking about how you're doing\" - Developer's Therapist</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242750/extras/60ce36da8ff05aa42f88082430597b5e.poster.avif?t=1774446792\" width=606 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242750/extras/60ce36da8ff05aa42f88082430597b5e.webm?t=1774446792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242750/extras/60ce36da8ff05aa42f88082430597b5e.mp4?t=1774446792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2-PLAYER MODE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live your lifelong dream of trolling friends and loved ones in an epic 2-player race to the door. Not only is each level somewhat unkind, but players can trigger even more unkinder traps on each other. So invite Grandma over and exact sweet revenge for her ambrosia salad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242750/extras/47fba31bacabf58e82b5299e473ec86b.poster.avif?t=1774446792\" width=608 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242750/extras/47fba31bacabf58e82b5299e473ec86b.webm?t=1774446792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com